YOU'RE DEAD.

00:06.350 --> 00:08.306
- ALEX IS THE VOLUNTEER
COORDINATOR HERE.

00:08.420 --> 00:09.648
- OH, HI.

00:09.760 --> 00:10.897
- I'M AN ALCOHOLIC.

00:11.010 --> 00:14.104
I'VE BEEN IN RECOVERY
FOR FIVE MONTHS.

00:14.220 --> 00:16.939
AND I'M TELLING YOU THIS
BECAUSE RELATIONSHIPS,

00:17.050 --> 00:20.838
ROMANTIC RELATIONSHIPS, JUST
AREN'T GOOD FOR ME RIGHT NOW.

00:20.950 --> 00:23.350
- OKAY, DREW,
PAY ATTENTION HERE.

00:23.470 --> 00:26.223
THIS IS, LIKE, A VERY IMPORTANT
MAN LESSON, SEE?

