PURGING.

00:30.090 --> 00:32.502
YOU GOT THE OLD, MISERABLE
DISGUSTING OIL--

00:32.610 --> 00:34.020
- YEAH, I CAN TELL.

00:34.130 --> 00:38.066
IT'S KINDA LIKE POPPING
A PIMPLE OR SOMETHING.

00:38.170 --> 00:40.092
- UGH, MAN, YOU GOTTA
GET OUTI'A MY HEAD.

