- WE'RE CHANGING THE OIL
IN THE BEAST.

00:46.700 --> 00:47.962
- WELL, I DON'T KNOW
HOW THAT'S GONNA LOOK

00:48.080 --> 00:49.069
IN A NOTE TO YOUR TEACHER.

00:49.180 --> 00:51.068
"DREW WAS CHANGING THE OIL

00:51.180 --> 00:52.932
IN A 60-YEAR-OLD TRACTOR
THAT BARELY RUNS."

00:53.050 --> 00:54.005
- YEAH, SHE'LL GET
GOING THOUGH.

00:54.120 --> 00:55.280
- YOU'RE A MESS.
GO CHANGE YOUR SHIRT.

00:55.400 --> 00:56.776
YOU LOOK LIKE YOU WORK
AT A GAS STATION.

00:56.880 --> 00:58.154
- OH, MAN.

00:58.260 --> 00:59.841
