I FORGOT ABOUT SCHOOL.

00:59.950 --> 01:01.531
I THINK--ARE THEY
STARTING EARLIER?

01:01.640 --> 01:03.460
- NO, DAD,
SAME OLD REGULAR TIME.

01:03.580 --> 01:04.979
- OH.

01:05.090 --> 01:06.955
- SO, UM,
WAS HE TALKING TO YOU?

01:07.060 --> 01:08.163
- OH, YEAH.

01:08.270 --> 01:10.886
YOU KNOW, I HAD TO TELL
HIM TO SHUT UP.

01:11.000 --> 01:12.069
- THANKS FOR SPENDING
TIME WITH HIM.

01:12.170 --> 01:13.967
- I LOVE HIM.

01:14.070 --> 01:15.094
HE'S MY GRANDSON,
YOU KNOW?

01:15.210 --> 01:16.791
I LOVE YOU,

01:16.900 --> 01:19.209
