ARE YOU GOING TO?

01:31.190 --> 01:33.841
- JENNA'S.

01:33.950 --> 01:35.679
- I DON'T KNOW--
- YES, YOU DO, MOM.

01:35.780 --> 01:37.054
- OKAY.
- OKAY, FINE?

01:37.160 --> 01:38.229
CAN I GO?

01:38.330 --> 01:39.774
- FINE.
CALL ME.

01:39.890 --> 01:42.029
- GREAT, THANKS.
SEE YOU.

01:42.130 --> 01:47.022
- I LOVE YOU.
- BYE.

