02:23.280 --> 02:24.656
- I THINK IT'S STUNNED.

02:24.760 --> 02:26.239
- WELL, WILL IT BE OKAY?

02:26.350 --> 02:27.681
- YEAH, SWEETIE,
IT'LL BE FINE.

02:27.800 --> 02:29.176
HEY, YOU KNOW, IF YOU GO
FIND A SHOE BOX,

02:29.280 --> 02:33.796
