THAT DEPENDENCE,

02:54.930 --> 02:56.989
YOU START
TO FEEL LIFE AGAIN.

02:57.100 --> 02:59.091
AND I'M HERE TO TELL YOU
THAT IT IS TRUE,

02:59.210 --> 03:01.201
THAT PIECE BY PIECE,
STEP BY STEP

03:01.310 --> 03:03.722
YOU START TO FEEL
YOUR LIFE COMING BACK.

03:03.830 --> 03:06.390
NOW, I MADE A FRIEND.

03:06.490 --> 03:11.280
AND SHE REALLY SHOWED ME
THAT I HAD SOMETHING TO OFFER.

03:11.390 --> 03:13.039
