03:42.840 --> 03:46.139
- I MEAN, THANK YOU
FOR LETTING ME COME.

03:54.230 --> 03:56.050
UM...

03:56.160 --> 03:58.913
YOUR FRIEND WHO YOU WERE
TALKING ABOUT,

03:59.030 --> 04:00.986
IT'S ME, RIGHT?

04:04.170 --> 04:06.377
- YES.

04:06.480 --> 04:09.893
OF COURSE IT IS.

