- I DIDN'T NOTICE.

06:11.470 --> 06:14.746
- JABBAR, YOU'VE GOT TO BE MORE
RESPONSIBLE WITH YOUR THINGS.

06:14.850 --> 06:16.784
PUT THEM AWAY WHEN
YOU'RE DONE USING THEM.

06:16.890 --> 06:18.096
- BUT I WASN'T
DONE USING THEM.

06:18.200 --> 06:20.373
- IF YOU'RE GOING TO BED,
YOU'RE DONE USING THEM.

06:20.480 --> 06:21.549
I NEED YOU
TO GET UP RIGHT NOW,

06:21.650 --> 06:23.333
GO IN THERE,
AND CLEAN UP YOUR ROOM.

