TO DO IT, YOU BETTER GO.

06:33.010 --> 06:34.557
- "I GUESS YOUR MOM
WANTS YOU TO"?

06:34.670 --> 06:36.285
WHAT'S THAT?
YOU SHOULD WANT HIM TO TOO.

06:36.390 --> 06:39.041
AND, BY THE WAY,
A SHRUG DOESN'T CONSTITUTE

06:39.150 --> 06:40.458
